name: India Summer
description:
My fourth Textual Inversion embedding!
Download the file and place it in the stable-diffusion-webui\embeddings folder.

The previews are done in deliberate_v11.

Add bs_indiasummer in your prompt to use her.

Trained on SD 1.5 so will only work with 1.5 models.

Shout out to https://civitai.com/user/dddokter for helping me test her!
